      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarpon_Springs%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1907, sponge merchants founded the Sponge Exchange, a non‑profit that stored sponges and hosted silent auctions.",
